
* Setup

    $ cd ~/scheme # Where '~/scheme' is the path to your Scheme libraries

    $ bzr branch lp:~scheme-libraries-team/scheme-libraries/srfi

    $ git clone git://github.com/dharmatech/agave.git

* Run a demo in Ypsilon

    $ ypsilon /usr/local/lib/ikarus/agave/demos/flexi-line.scm

* Run a demo in Ikarus

    $ ikarus --r6rs-script /usr/local/lib/ikarus/agave/demos/flexi-line.scm

* Make a demo load faster in Ikarus

    $ ikarus --compile-dependencies /usr/local/lib/ikarus/agave/demos/flexi-line.scm
